{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.1","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:1","prev_osis_id":"Gen.019.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">S\u00e9jour d\u2019Abraham \u00e0 Gu\u00e9rar<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-18: cf. (Ge 12:10-20; 26:1-11.) Ps 105:12-15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Abraham partit de l\u00e0 pour la contr\u00e9e du midi; il s\u2019\u00e9tablit entre Kad\u00e8s et Schur, et fit un s\u00e9jour \u00e0 Gu\u00e9rar.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.2","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.19.38","name":"Gen\u00e8se 19:38","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.19.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.2","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:2","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Abraham disait de Sara, sa femme: C\u2019est ma s\u0153ur. Abim\u00e9lec, roi de Gu\u00e9rar, fit enlever Sara.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.3","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.1","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.3","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:3","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Alors Dieu apparut en songe \u00e0 Abim\u00e9lec pendant la nuit, et lui dit: Voici, tu vas mourir \u00e0 cause de la femme que tu as enlev\u00e9e, car elle a un mari.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.4","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.2","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.4","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:4","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Abim\u00e9lec, qui ne s\u2019\u00e9tait point approch\u00e9 d\u2019elle, r\u00e9pondit: Seigneur, ferais-tu p\u00e9rir m\u00eame une nation juste?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.5","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.3","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.5","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:5","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ne m\u2019a-t-il pas dit: C\u2019est ma s\u0153ur? Et elle-m\u00eame n\u2019a-t-elle pas dit: C\u2019est mon fr\u00e8re? J\u2019ai agi avec un c\u0153ur pur et avec des mains innocentes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.6","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.4","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.6","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:6","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Dieu lui dit en songe: Je sais que tu as agi avec un c\u0153ur pur; aussi t\u2019ai-je emp\u00each\u00e9 de p\u00e9cher contre moi. C\u2019est pourquoi je n\u2019ai pas permis que tu la touchasses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.7","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.5","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.7","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:7","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Maintenant, rends la femme de cet homme; car il est proph\u00e8te, il priera pour toi, et tu vivras. Mais, si tu ne la rends pas, sache que tu mourras, toi et tout ce qui t\u2019appartient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.8","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.6","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.8","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:8","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Abim\u00e9lec se leva de bon matin, il appela tous ses serviteurs, et leur rapporta toutes ces choses; et ces gens furent saisis d\u2019une grande frayeur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.9","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.7","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.9","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:9","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Abim\u00e9lec appela aussi Abraham, et lui dit: Qu\u2019est-ce que tu nous as fait? Et en quoi t\u2019ai-je offens\u00e9, que tu aies fait venir sur moi et sur mon royaume un si grand p\u00e9ch\u00e9? Tu as commis \u00e0 mon \u00e9gard des actes qui ne doivent pas se commettre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.10","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.8","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.10","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:10","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Et Abim\u00e9lec dit \u00e0 Abraham: Quelle intention avais-tu pour agir de la sorte?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.11","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.9","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.11","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:11","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Abraham r\u00e9pondit: Je me disais qu\u2019il n\u2019y avait sans doute aucune crainte de Dieu dans ce pays, et que l\u2019on me tuerait \u00e0 cause de ma femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.12","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.10","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.12","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:12","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>De plus, il est vrai qu\u2019elle est ma s\u0153ur, fille de mon p\u00e8re; seulement, elle n\u2019est pas fille de ma m\u00e8re; et elle est devenue ma femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.13","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.11","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.13","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:13","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Lorsque Dieu me fit errer loin de la maison de mon p\u00e8re, je dis \u00e0 Sara: Voici la gr\u00e2ce que tu me feras; dans tous les lieux o\u00f9 nous irons, dis de moi: C\u2019est mon fr\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.14","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.12","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.14","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:14","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Abim\u00e9lec prit des brebis et des b\u0153ufs, des serviteurs et des servantes, et les donna \u00e0 Abraham; et il lui rendit Sara, sa femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.15","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.13","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.15","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:15","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Abim\u00e9lec dit: Voici, mon pays est devant toi; demeure o\u00f9 il te plaira.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.16","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.14","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.16","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:16","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Et il dit \u00e0 Sara: Voici, je donne \u00e0 ton fr\u00e8re mille pi\u00e8ces d\u2019argent; cela te sera un voile sur les yeux pour tous ceux qui sont avec toi, et aupr\u00e8s de tous tu seras justifi\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.17","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.15","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.17","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:17","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.020.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Abraham pria Dieu, et Dieu gu\u00e9rit Abim\u00e9lec, sa femme et ses servantes; et elles purent enfanter.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.18","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.16","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.18","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 20:18","prev_osis_id":"Gen.020.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.021.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.20.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Car l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait frapp\u00e9 de st\u00e9rilit\u00e9 toute la maison d\u2019Abim\u00e9lec, \u00e0 cause de Sara, femme d\u2019Abraham.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.21.1","name":"Gen\u00e8se 21:1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.21.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.20.17","name":"Gen\u00e8se 20:17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.20.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81e51335ad7.83641464');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81e51335ad7.83641464\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81e51335ad7.83641464","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81e51335ad7.83641464'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81e51335ad7.83641464\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}